cu.explanation_en: Setting the local S port C to 0 is out of range for valid port numbers and will cause socket binding failure, preventing F1 interface communication.

du.explanation_en: Setting the local N port C to 0 is out of range for valid port numbers and will cause connection failure for F1 interface.
du.explanation_zh: 將本地 N 端口 C 設定為 0 超出有效端口號範圍，會導致 F1 介面的連接失敗。
